        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. The global production volume is extrapolated from the German and US production volumes of trinexapac using the global average GDP (constant 2017 international USD from 2015-2019). The annual production value of Germany in the year 2017 is 631250 kg and the US production volume in 2017 is 11.8 kg. This value is divided by the German share of global GDP, 3.57% (2015-2019), and the US share, 16.00% (2015-2019).
References:
Bundesamt für Verbraucherschutz und Lebensmittelsicherheit (2018): Absatz an Pflanzenschutzmitteln in der Bundesrepublik Deutschland 2017, available here: https://www.bvl.bund.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/04_Pflanzenschutzmittel/01_meldungen_par_64/meld_par_64_2017.pdf?__blob=publicationFile&amp;v=2, accessed 07-06-2022.
U.S. Geological Survey (2018): Estimated Annual Agricultural Pesticide Use, available here: https://water.usgs.gov/nawqa/pnsp/usage/maps/county-level/, accessed 07-06-2022.
World bank (2022): GDP, available here:  https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.PP.KD, accessed 17-05-2022.</productionVolumeComment>
