        <unitName xml:lang="en">MJ</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature data published by the GENDORF Chemical Park. The factory produced an average of 2462760 tonnes of chemical substances (including intermediates) per year in the years 2015-2019. The average consumption of natural gas in the years 2015-2019 was 4645920000 MJ per year. This equals 1.8865 MJ/kg chemical produced.
